# Tech Stack

| Layer         | Technology                                                          |
| ------------- | ------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| Framework     | Expo SDK 54, React Native 0.81                                      |
| Routing       | Expo Router 6 (file-based)                                          |
| Language      | TypeScript (strict mode)                                            |
| Styling       | Uniwind + Tailwind CSS 4 (`className` prop)                         |
| Blockchain    | Solana via `@solana/kit`, `@wallet-ui/react-native-kit`             |
| Data Fetching | `@tanstack/react-query`                                             |
| State         | Zustand (with AsyncStorage persist middleware)                      |
| Storage       | `@react-native-async-storage/async-storage` (via `@/utils/storage`) |
| Notifications | `react-native-toast-message`                                        |
| Splash Screen | `expo-splash-screen`                                                |

## Key Patterns

- All providers wrapped in `<AppProviders>` (see `src/components/app-providers.tsx`)
- Theme: Uniwind (`Uniwind.setTheme()`, `useUniwind()`) + `<AppTheme>` for early hydration; navigation theme via `useAppTheme()` in `_layout.tsx`
- Wallet connection via `useMobileWallet()` from `@wallet-ui/react-native-kit`
- Wallet actions via `useWalletActions()` from `@/hooks/useWalletActions`
- Toast: `import Toast from 'react-native-toast-message'` then `Toast.show({ type, text1, text2 })`
